Document: ## Baked Goods -Bun = Microwave 1 Dough Slice for 5 seconds -Bread = Microwave 1 Dough for 10 seconds -Baguette = Microwave 1 Dough + 5u Table Salt + 5u Pepper for 15 seconds -Crostini = Slice Baguette -Banana Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 1 Banana for 15 seconds -Cornbread = Microwave Cornmeal Dough for 10 seconds -Cream Cheese Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 2 Cheese Wedges + 5u Milk for 15 seconds -Meat Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 2 Raw Cutlets + 2 Cheese Wedges for 15 seconds -mimana Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 1 Mimana + 5u Nothing for 15 seconds -Sausage Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 1 Raw Meat for 15 seconds -Spider Meat Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 2 Raw Spider Cutlets + 2 Cheese Wedges for 15 seconds -Tofu Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 1 Tofu for 15 seconds -Xeno Meat Bread = Microwave 1 Dough + 2 Raw Xeno Cutlets + 2 Cheese Wedges for 15 seconds -Buttered Toast = Microwave 1 Bread Slice + 1 Stick of Butter for 5 seconds -French Toast = Microwave 1 Bread Slice + 5u Milk + 12u egg for 5 seconds -Garlic Bread Slice = Microwave 1 Bread Slice + 1 Garlic + 1 Stick of Butter for 5 seconds -Jelly Toast = Microwave 1 Bread Slice + 1 Amanita Jelly for 5 seconds -Moldy Bread Slice = Microwave 1 Bread Slice + 1 Fly Amanita for 5 seconds -Two Slice = Microwave 2 Bread Slices + 5u wine for 5 seconds -Bread Dog = Microwave 1 Sausage Bread + 1 Animal Heart + 1 Cooked Spaceshroom + 5u Cognizine for 15 seconds
